<topic template="Default" lasteditedby="Adam" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>TOP-TIPS</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Top-Tips ONLY</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">TOP-TIPS</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">This topic includes all of the best <text styleclass="VariableName">Top-Tips</text> to be published when it has more than five. </para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">Top-Tip 1<text styleclass="Body Text"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Save you model</text><text styleclass="Body Text">...</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName">A: Save new model immediately</text><text styleclass="Body Text">: then Auto-Save will also start immediately.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName">B: CTRL+S</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to save the latest major change.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName">C: Save as ...</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> NEW model-name if you open a model you do not want to change. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:2px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">Top-Tip 2<text styleclass="Body Text"> : When to set </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">CYCLES / Min = 0</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> :</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">CYCLES / MIN = 0.0001</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to design </text>stationary<text styleclass="Body Text"> mechanisms.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text">For example: Scissor Lift, Guard Balancing, Counter-weight Balancing.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text">When the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Cycling Speed = ~0</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Inertia</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Centrifugal</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Coriolis</text><text styleclass="Body Text">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName">forces = ~0.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:2px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">Top-Tip 3<text styleclass="Body Text"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">RIGHT-CLICK to SELECT and OK the Command-Manager.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Right-click the LAST (or ONLY) element for the Command-Manager, you will select the element AND complete the command. </para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">For example: <text styleclass="T_Menu">Click ADD Trace-Point: </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Right-Click a Point</text> - to select the Point AND complete the command - and there is the Trace-Point.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:2px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">Top-Tip 4<text styleclass="Body Text"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Use CAPS and lower-case motion-names</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">For example:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">CAPS</text> for motion-names that act on real parts in the model</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">lower-case</text> for motion-names that are for visual-effects, or not used anywhere in the model.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
